    "name": "超合金冲击 Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3092480,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/641afc681bed68973c846ae9a40285ee.avif?t=1769068819\" width=600 height=185 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>游戏简介</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在超合金宇宙中，游侠号的所有人要去寻找终极的宇宙宝藏星球AE-38。而旅途中的阻碍者和竞争者们，就由宇宙猎人牧（贰号）和凯里他们统统踢飞吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含横版过关+Roguelike 狂潮战斗的2D格斗动作游戏！体验拳拳到肉的宇宙冒险，组队配合连击、超必杀技，一起打败强敌——两位宇宙猎人已严阵以待！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/9b63d46482d1755ee007b66d23a77cdf.poster.avif?t=1769068819\" width=1068 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/9b63d46482d1755ee007b66d23a77cdf.webm?t=1769068819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/9b63d46482d1755ee007b66d23a77cdf.mp4?t=1769068819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/2b86374f9b1ff3e3d91b6d6bee781d22.avif?t=1769068819\" width=600 height=185 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>游戏模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏主要由下面几个游玩模式构成： <br><strong>故事模式 | </strong>探索宝藏星球，解锁剧情与角色之谜</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战斗狂潮 | </strong>每局都是新生！百种强化构建无敌流派</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>终极挑战 | </strong>挑战最难的战斗证明你的实力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/17362c222330e98b7ef66508a24b2837.poster.avif?t=1769068819\" width=1068 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/17362c222330e98b7ef66508a24b2837.webm?t=1769068819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/17362c222330e98b7ef66508a24b2837.mp4?t=1769068819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/9861a9e0289ba08f4b26b6b51944347b.avif?t=1769068819\" width=600 height=185 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>角色和强化</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>【核心体验】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身两名风格迥异的宇宙猎人：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>牧</strong>： 使用能量爪近战格斗的机器人，拥有灵活敏捷的身手击飞敌人，在空中使用连续技和战斗战技追击敌人造成大量伤害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>凯里</strong>： 使用各种枪械与体术战斗的强化人，是需要一定操作技巧、可以支配战场的上级者向角色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/6631f289600d4d4f4e00d0ebe20c573f.poster.avif?t=1769068819\" width=1068 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/6631f289600d4d4f4e00d0ebe20c573f.webm?t=1769068819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/6631f289600d4d4f4e00d0ebe20c573f.mp4?t=1769068819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>深度Build定制</strong>：每名角色50+战技×上百芯片组合打造专属战斗流派</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>支援系统</strong>：随身调查船战备点复活+支援者战场辅助，逆转绝境！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/0a18a14c51ff1883b58803d7a22ee52c.poster.avif?t=1769068819\" width=1068 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/0a18a14c51ff1883b58803d7a22ee52c.webm?t=1769068819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/0a18a14c51ff1883b58803d7a22ee52c.mp4?t=1769068819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/be6b735e9a252e210d379c686d99d00c.avif?t=1769068819\" width=600 height=185 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>战场和敌人</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >属性进攻寻找弱点，机械类弱电、生物类怕燃烧，利用场景物品获得战斗优势！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/9820ef261b940340bf7ea632fc03ce19.poster.avif?t=1769068819\" width=1068 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/9820ef261b940340bf7ea632fc03ce19.webm?t=1769068819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/9820ef261b940340bf7ea632fc03ce19.mp4?t=1769068819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>头目敌人</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与玩家角色对等的强大存在。他们也能在战斗中累积超能并释放强大必杀技。面对其强大攻势，趁招式破绽集中攻击可击溃其体势，打断进攻夺取优势！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/d5d01fc0b063aefea83642a579c2289a.poster.avif?t=1769068819\" width=1068 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/d5d01fc0b063aefea83642a579c2289a.webm?t=1769068819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/d5d01fc0b063aefea83642a579c2289a.mp4?t=1769068819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/291db2978ce3d40377f77ae50d0489e5.avif?t=1769068819\" width=600 height=185 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>丰富的游戏内容</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 每名角色拥有五十多种战技与特殊动作自由搭配 <br>• 芯片栏自由调整角色性能：空中多段跳/无限能量/多重生命值由你决定 <br>• 收集全部支援者让战斗更有趣 <br>• 数十种敌人及多样BOSS可供挑战 <br>• 战斗狂潮模式含上百种强化内容助你毁天灭地 <br>无论单人还是多人游玩，每次打开游戏都能享受爽快尽兴的战斗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/4f2f5c7a7c3242bd535630162326fcf4.poster.avif?t=1769068819\" width=1068 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/4f2f5c7a7c3242bd535630162326fcf4.webm?t=1769068819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/4f2f5c7a7c3242bd535630162326fcf4.mp4?t=1769068819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/32e8d66f2f07031d0ddf0e2f7a289eda.poster.avif?t=1769068819\" width=1068 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/32e8d66f2f07031d0ddf0e2f7a289eda.webm?t=1769068819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092480/extras/32e8d66f2f07031d0ddf0e2f7a289eda.mp4?t=1769068819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
